{"id":231716199,"title":"關於細粉率","content":"想必大家在看磨豆機或聽人講解時一定聽過細粉率，但你知道在咖啡研磨與萃取上，細粉率一詞並不全面嗎？\n\n不全面的原因有以下幾點：\n\n1.細粉率會跟以什麼標準篩除細粉有關，以多少um做為細粉的分界，會關係到篩出來的細粉屬於主要的分佈，或是研磨過程的微小細粉。\nhttps://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg\n\n2.最重要的是粒徑分佈（Particle Size Distribution），以萃取來說，位於Peak附近的粉貢獻整體萃取率較多，試想：「細粉量少卻分佈較散」和「細粉量稍多卻分佈集中」兩種情況，何者萃取均勻度較高呢？\nhttps://i.imgur.com/8ATbOua.jpg\n圖片來源：Mahlkonig\n\n\n分享些個人經驗，目前我使用的磨豆機是Helor 102 (Robur 83mm) 和 Forte BG ，在萃取上BG可以做到更高的萃取，原因不只是它細粉較少，而是BG的粒徑分佈較集中。","excerpt":"想必大家在看磨豆機或聽人講解時一定聽過細粉率，但你知道在咖啡研磨與萃取上，細粉率一詞並不全面嗎？不全面的原因有以下幾點：1.細粉率會跟以什麼標準篩除細粉有關，以多少um做為細粉的分界，會關係到篩出來的","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6120536f-6a70-49bb-8891-ec0ba2f4b396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-07-21T16:38:42.121Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-21T17:33:13.986Z","commentCount":10,"likeCount":17,"tags":[],"topics":["咖啡","磨豆機","手沖咖啡","精品咖啡"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"咖啡","forumAlias":"coffee","school":"東吳大學","department":"經濟學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":17}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/8ATbOua.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"71557f18-ee6c-46ed-89ba-9980441ae5ae","url":"https://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-07-21T16:38:42.121Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-21T17:33:13.986Z"},{"id":"71557f18-ee6c-46ed-89ba-9980441ae5ae","url":"https://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yiSx8a2.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-07-21T16:38:42.